{"tid":1009744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣挑戰「中毒唇、小丑裝」網友大讚：這種風格也能駕馭得很好！","createTime":"2019-02-05T11:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T03:54:27.000Z","uid":9573,"like":16,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"30004ed2f7db0dd41884668cd6a5b930fd1c9859","tid":1009744,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T11:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/O57vLLzAWECSzf5H3tntAw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/85c89a8701bb26447a1840b56dfafca9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FO57vLLzAWECSzf5H3tntAw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F85c89a8701bb26447a1840b56dfafca9&h=2e5dd4e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣最新時尚大片挑戰出道以來最狂造型！<br />\n有「國民老婆」、「治癒系女神」之稱的日本人氣女星新垣結衣，在全新的一年，皆連3個月登上《NYLON JAPAN》雜誌，憑著逆天顏值大膽挑戰超難駕馭的造型，令人耳目一新！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tBxVEikTQFqavaDk82RD8g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/d7f2920fb75f8d26f2eff5c1894b4f15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtBxVEikTQFqavaDk82RD8g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fd7f2920fb75f8d26f2eff5c1894b4f15&h=b96dbffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身高近170公分、模特出身的新垣結衣，有著天使臉孔、窈窕的高挑身材，近來為日本版《NYLON JAPAN》雜誌拍攝「Awesome Girl」單元，嘗試各種前衛造型，突破自我形象！在1月份時尚大片中，新垣結衣頭戴黑色網紗帽、穿著淺藍色長版大衣、手拿捧花，渾身散發詭譎神祕的氣息；或穿上酒紅色毛衣、藉由身後的挖背設計，展露性感風情狂圈粉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rKeRfxf5mwJwTRDj_bGsXw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/5f8d2ffcfb43e73357901855cf621f4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrKeRfxf5mwJwTRDj_bGsXw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F5f8d2ffcfb43e73357901855cf621f4d&h=ca75ff09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在最新曝光的2月份美照中，新垣結衣身穿英國時尚達人Alex Chung同名品牌薄紗透視格紋洋裝、混搭黑白菱格紋長襪，化身鬼靈精怪的「小丑女」，整體造型搶眼吸睛；或頂著泡麵頭、畫上藍色中毒唇，挑戰出道以來最狂造型，粉絲看了覺得新鮮有趣，狂讚：「酷老婆上線」、「這種風格也能駕馭得很好！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/51200797_1165585610288898_9136240297313828864_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=fba8cf447a13b8a2c3d651f83de1712a&amp;oe=5CFA8CFE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F51200797_1165585610288898_9136240297313828864_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Dfba8cf447a13b8a2c3d651f83de1712a%26oe%3D5CFA8CFE&h=0e5a2a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在接下來的3月，新垣結衣再度恢復成大家所熟悉的鄰家女孩模樣，穿著Oversize毛衣、大秀纖長美腿，展現慵懶又撩人的一面；或穿上綠色印花洋裝、搭配鮮豔紅外套，以俏麗復古風Look呼應女神清新甜美的氣質！"},{"pid":"00fb959a507b53dfa92bb36f4af32252ac848c93","tid":1009744,"uid":12178,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUMk1Qm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUMk1Qm.png&h=0a8ff7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJOJO?"},{"pid":"11a80b4af45f8be1ac25ab25c8e698d2eadd4404","tid":1009744,"uid":6562,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"我係特燈黎睇千雪bb ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f681c7bb3b1efead55aa140ebe57a7227aa56c9","tid":1009744,"uid":73722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"朱千雪讓我下沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773bea2f36af001f1b17d6f41c31de9f46f98695","tid